<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62a48ed0-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s2705"><num value="2705">§ 2705.</num><heading> Powers of Chairman</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="id62a48ed1-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s2705/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><chapeau> The Chairman, on behalf of the Commission, shall have power, subject to an appeal to the Commission, to—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id62a48ed2-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s2705/a/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> issue orders of temporary closure of gaming activities as provided in <ref href="/us/usc/t25/s2713/b">section 2713(b) of this title</ref>;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id62a6d7c3-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s2705/a/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> levy and collect civil fines as provided in <ref href="/us/usc/t25/s2713/a">section 2713(a) of this title</ref>;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id62a6d7c4-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s2705/a/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> approve tribal ordinances or resolutions regulating class II gaming and class III gaming as provided in <ref href="/us/usc/t25/s2710">section 2710 of this title</ref>; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id62a6d7c5-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s2705/a/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> approve management contracts for class II gaming and class III gaming as provided in sections 2710(d)(9) and 2711 of this title.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="id62a6d7c6-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s2705/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content> The Chairman shall have such other powers as may be delegated by the Commission.</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id62a6d7c7-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/497/s6">Pub. L. 100–497, § 6</ref>, <date date="1988-10-17">Oct. 17, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/2470">102 Stat. 2470</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
